<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />復活節<delay8 />玩得開心嗎？<delay40 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在今天找回童心，<delay20 />像個孩子一樣
收集蛋<delay8 />也不錯呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">那個，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你已經見過<delay8 /><colour id="3" />蹦蹦<colour id="65535" />了嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要看著他，<delay8 />就能深切地感受到
他想要盛大慶祝復活節的心情，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />連我也覺得很開心呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />不過，<delay8 />他有時候一臉疲倦的樣子，<delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓我有點擔心呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，你知道嗎？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />復活節的蛋是一種點心喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這麼可愛的蛋，<delay8 />吃下去是有點浪費，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，你也很想知道
它吃起來是什麼味道吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那些飛在天空上的氣球呀，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天是不是<delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比往常還要多啊？<pageBreak />我很想靠近一點看看，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過怎麼伸手也碰不到呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />怎樣才能把它射下來呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />剛才<delay8 />我在沙灘上
撿到了一個可愛的瓶中信。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到底<delay8 />是誰放進海裡的呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />漂來一些跟平常不一樣的東西，<delay20 />
有種驚喜的感覺，讓人很高興呢。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是裡面<delay8 />也很驚喜就好了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">真不愧是復活節，<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天飄在島上的氣球<delay20 />
都設計成蛋的樣子呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道那個能不能吃呢<tag a="110" b="0" />？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呃，討厭啦！<delay20 />我，<delay8 />我可不是<delay20 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />肚子餓了喔？！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />剛剛嚇了我一跳<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay40 />我看見樹上
有沒看過的水果，所以就搖了一下。<delay20 />
<anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到竟然有蛋掉下來！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是不可思議啊！<delay40 />
不過，<delay8 />我還以為會打到頭，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />捏了一把冷汗呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />欸，<delay8 />我跟你說喔！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />剛才我在釣魚，竟然釣到了蛋！<delay40 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到底<delay8 />是什麼蛋呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說是魚卵，好像又太大了，<delay20 />
不過，<delay8 />竟然能從水裡釣上來<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay8 />真是神秘啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="110" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="110_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
我很高興能在復活節見到你喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一起努力地<delay20 />尋找蛋吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="110_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有好好地享受復活節嗎？<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />節慶就是得盡情享受才行喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="111" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />我問你，<delay frames="40" />
如果你願意的話，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要不要和我交換蛋呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想用<colour id="1" />3顆<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><colour id="65535" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來交換你身上同數量的<delay8 />
<colour id="1" />其他種類的蛋<colour id="65535" />！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="111_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">好啊！</message>
	<message label="111_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">抱歉喔</message>
	<message label="112" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00">話說<tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要不要<delay8 />跟我交換蛋呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我用<colour id="1" />3顆<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><colour id="65535" /><delay20 />
來交換<delay8 />你身上<colour id="1" />3顆其他種類的蛋<colour id="65535" />，
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你覺得這樣如何呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="112_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">來交換吧！</message>
	<message label="112_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">恕我拒絕</message>
	<message label="113" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼<delay8 />請告訴我<delay20 />
你想用哪種蛋來做交換吧？</message>
	<message label="114" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />太好了～<delay20 />果然試著問問是正確的決定！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那麼<delay20 />你想用哪種蛋來跟我做交換呢？</message>
	<message label="116" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />謝謝你！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />復活節<delay8 />真是一個能感受到
人間處處有溫情的活動呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="117" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從<tag a="110" b="4" />那交換來的蛋<delay20 />
真是令人捨不得使用啊。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="118" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay20 />不行嗎？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒關係，<delay20 />你不用在意喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="119" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay20 />真可惜<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />向你提出這種任性的要求，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是抱歉呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="120" attrib="00 00 02 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我的<colour id="1" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><colour id="65535" />，
和你的<colour id="1" /><tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x1" /><colour id="65535" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />互相拿出<colour id="1" />3顆<colour id="65535" />做交換沒錯吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="120_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">OK！</message>
	<message label="120_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">還是算了</message>
	<message label="121" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也OK喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那我們<delay20 />就來交換吧！</message>
	<message label="122" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />你的口袋裝得滿滿的，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣不就沒辦法收下
我要給你的蛋嗎<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />抱歉，<delay frames="40" />這件事<delay20 />就當作沒發生過吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過我之後還是有可能會<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再來拜託你喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>